name: Merissa Burton
text: Very clean! Amazing pizza 🍕 . Great service   they are all very nice and helpful  . 5 stars pizza hut 👍👍👍👏👏👏👏

name: Cp powell
text: Fabulous,clean,staff is very well mannered,gave me options of what I asked for and more ,will definitely go back I give them 10 stars if you had them.

name: Mike Ratliff
text: Good food definitely just had the pzone and definitely going back again

name: Amy Nevels
text: Always on time taste delicious very polite crowd

name: Tammy Musson
text: The staff at this location is AWESOME! And there's a young man named Skyler that works there. He is professional, courteous and SO very helpful.  There's a particular pizza that my son and I LOVE, and it's always made just right!  I would recommend this location to all pizza lovers!!!

name: Jess-MommaMoore
text: Staff is great. Food is great. Make sure you have all the sauces you ordered though.

name: Travis Jones
text: So we called in an big box order for 2 deep dish pizzas. Didnt get the big box just 2 separate boxes. Didnt get deep dish got pan. And it wasn't even cooked all the way. Also order an extra sauce but they never put it in the order.

name: Karen Thompson
text: Great pizza no inside dining or delivery tho

name: April Powell
text: Cleanest pizza hut we have ever been in ,I give it 10 stars against all the pizza restaurants in vermilion county, very polite worker Sarah and she had a smile .You go to othe pizza places and there rude or give you dirty looks

name: Mowhawk Man
text: Very friendly staff on time pickups food was better than before but still could use some improvement light on the toppings crust was Bland breadsticks had no parmesan seasoning

text: This a good place to get pizzas it is clean and friendly to
